address2: Room 1907-1909, 19th Floor No. 1 East Chang An Avenue Dong Cheng District
longBusinessSummary: InvesTech Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the network system integration, professional network services, and mobile software platform businesses. The company's network system integration services comprise enterprise Internet architecture, high-speed IP bearer network architecture, data center and storage program, optical transmission network, wireless coverage program, application delivery program, security interconnection and access monitoring program, and network management program. Its professional network services include network system services comprising preparation, planning, design, implementation, operation, maintenance, and optimization; network planning, design, and project management services; and network system maintenance services, such as network operation and maintenance, management and security, hosting, evaluation, consultation and performance test, design and integration services, etc. The company also offers smart office suite software solutions; and rents network equipment. It operates in Mainland China, Vietnam, Hong Kong, the United States, and internationally. The company was formerly known as HL Technology Group Limited and changed its name to InvesTech Holdings Limited in June 2016. InvesTech Holdings Limited was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
